{"tid":2235493,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[提防放負風向]  目前抗爭係因時制宜變陣，有效程度同士氣一直冇減弱過","createTime":"2020-10-08T17:19:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-09T17:50:16.000Z","uid":173326,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5bc88e00e49ae0307fea6004b4bee13e4a0404d6","tid":2235493,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T17:19:29.000Z","msg":"街頭上，法庭聲援、拘留所聲援、聲援被捕人士街站、定期悼念，從來冇停止過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n網絡上，twitter每個鐘都大把新post打國際線，用嚟connect藏維蒙，仲有美國政壇日日都好多人tweet屌中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n隔離仲有人日日開tvb狙擊post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n經濟上，藍營蝕到賣底褲都唔掂，而黃圈成功留住香港人嘅資金去為香港人提供商品、就業機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"large\">而目前最急、最打擊到中共又唔洗錢嘅，莫過於德國制裁支那嘅聯署，10月20日限期前要有5萬人簽署。<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"orange\">德國議會聯署 (德文)</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/35Z4LDD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F35Z4LDD&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusr52AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=2b919853\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/35Z4LDD</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">教學：如何用Chrome Google Translate 簽名</span></strong> <br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2EOgauK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2EOgauK&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusr52AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=7c13f620\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2EOgauK</a>"},{"pid":"6c994edde19f6f9ab9d554c45e19364be020ca44","tid":2235493,"uid":173326,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T17:20:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/frances.huiwingting/videos/776349853204218\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffrances.huiwingting%2Fvideos%2F776349853204218&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusr52AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=f1feefe8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/frances.huiwingting/videos/776349853204218</a><br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n❗️如果聯署在10月20日前得到五萬個簽名，德國議會便要就制裁中國舉行聆訊，但到現時聯署還是只有一萬個簽名。<br />\n幫大家整理了一下，希望大家明白這個聯署的重要性。請立刻參與聯署！<br />\n＊ ＊ ＊<br />\n德國議會聯署：(德文)<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/35Z4LDD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F35Z4LDD&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusr52AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=2b919853\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/35Z4LDD</a><br />\nPetition Details 聯署內容:<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2ZZxtAD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ZZxtAD&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusr52AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=500cf05c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2ZZxtAD</a> (中文)<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3478FYL\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3478FYL&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusr52AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=2312830f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3478FYL</a> (ENG)<br />\n<br />\n【德國戰線聯署】絲打拍埋片教你點簽！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2231070\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2231070</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6164c20bc7cad45d34b9388bb531c959d1bd72f9","tid":2235493,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T17:25:08.000Z","msg":"留名睇藍絲唔抵得黃圈而話經濟行為唔算抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/clean.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好文推介：<br />\n不助長中共經濟實力便是一種抗爭<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>很清楚中共的一種主要傲慢是：你想來中國賺錢，閉嘴和跪低吧！說到底這是經濟實力所助長的霸氣，因此，支持其經濟發展就是支撐其霸權；反之，不參與其經濟已經算是一種抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n高興聽到有丹麥養老基金公司於其官網公布，「由於中國持續侵犯人權，故將中國在其投資組合中剔除」；該基金支持「平衡回報及責任」的運作理念，「由於要承擔社會責任，故必須對中國撤資」。</blockquote><br />\n<span class=\"x-small\"><a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%B8%8D%E5%8A%A9%E9%95%B7%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E5%AF%A6%E5%8A%9B%E4%BE%BF%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E7%A8%AE%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD/\" d